      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "feat(webui): add session workspace rail",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Replace the old right-rail agent file list with a session-scoped workspace rail showing changed files, read files, artifacts, and project browser entries.\n- Add `sessions.files.list` / `sessions.files.get` Gateway RPCs and protocol schemas so the UI can load session-touched files and bounded previews.\n- Keep the rail collapsible, keep file previews inside the chat workbench, and preserve split-pane resizing without letting the preview/sidebar overlap the composer.\n- Harden session file reads with workspace-root containment, `fs-safe` bounded reads, symlink-parent rejection, search traversal limits, browser-only preview denial, canonical agent workspace fallback, and nested `spawnedCwd` path handling.\n\n## Before / After\n\n### Before\n\nOld rail only exposed a generic agent workspace file list and did not provide session-scoped changed/read/artifact/project context.\n\n![Before session rail](https://github.com/Solvely-Colin/openclaw/releases/download/session-workspace-rail-proof/before-session-rail.gif)\n\n### After\n\nNew drawer is session-scoped, collapsible, supports file/artifact previews, project browsing, and stays contained beside chat.\n\n![After session workspace rail](https://github.com/Solvely-Colin/openclaw/releases/download/session-workspace-rail-proof/after-session-workspace-rail.gif)\n\nProof assets are hosted on the fork release: https://github.com/Solvely-Colin/openclaw/releases/tag/session-workspace-rail-proof\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\n**Behavior or issue addressed:** Session workspace rail lists session-touched files, browser context, and artifacts while limiting `sessions.files.get` previews to transcript-touched files under the resolved workspace boundary.\n\n**Real environment tested:** Local OpenClaw Gateway from this branch on macOS, isolated temp state/config, loopback auth-none Gateway on port `19155`, with a seeded real session transcript and workspace.\n\n**Exact steps or command run after this patch:**\n\n- `OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR=$PROOF_ROOT/state OPENCLAW_CONFIG_PATH=$PROOF_ROOT/openclaw.json OPENCLAW_SKIP_CHANNELS=1 pnpm openclaw gateway run --force --auth none --port 19155 --allow-unconfigured --ws-log compact`\n- `pnpm openclaw gateway call sessions.files.list --json --params '{\"sessionKey\":\"agent:main:main\",\"path\":\"ui\"}'`\n- `pnpm openclaw gateway call sessions.files.get --json --params '{\"sessionKey\":\"agent:main:main\",\"path\":\"package.json\"}'`\n- `pnpm openclaw gateway call sessions.files.get --json --params '{\"sessionKey\":\"agent:main:main\",\"path\":\"ui/vite.config.ts\"}'`\n\n**Evidence after fix:**\n\n`sessions.files.list` returned a real workspace root and both session-touched and browser-only rows:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"root\": \"/tmp/openclaw-session-rail-proof.QGzHSW/workspace\",\n  \"files\": [\n    { \"path\": \"package.json\", \"kind\": \"modified\", \"missing\": false },\n    { \"path\": \"ui/chat.ts\", \"kind\": \"modified\", \"missing\": false },\n    { \"path\": \"src/readme.md\", \"kind\": \"read\", \"missing\": false }\n  ],\n  \"browser\": {\n    \"path\": \"ui\",\n    \"entries\": [\n      { \"path\": \"ui/chat.ts\", \"kind\": \"file\", \"sessionKind\": \"modified\" },\n      { \"path\": \"ui/vite.config.ts\", \"kind\": \"file\" }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\nTouched file preview succeeded:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"root\": \"/tmp/openclaw-session-rail-proof.QGzHSW/workspace\",\n  \"file\": {\n    \"path\": \"package.json\",\n    \"kind\": \"modified\",\n    \"missing\": false,\n    \"content\": \"{\\\"name\\\":\\\"session-rail-proof\\\"}\\n\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\nBrowser-only preview was denied:\n\n```text\nGateway call failed: GatewayClientRequestError: session file not found\n```\n\n**Observed result after fix:** The real Gateway returned session workspace data with changed/read files and browser rows, returned content for touched `package.json`, and denied browser-only `ui/vite.config.ts` preview.\n\n**What was not tested:** Live provider/model turn generation; proof used seeded local session state and skipped channel sidecars.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `pnpm lint --threads=8`\n- `pnpm test src/gateway/server-methods/sessions-files.test.ts ui/src/ui/views/chat.test.ts ui/src/ui/chat/sidebar-session-picker.browser.test.ts -- --reporter=verbose`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run --config test/vitest/vitest.ui-e2e.config.ts --configLoader runner ui/src/ui/e2e/chat-flow.e2e.test.ts`\n- `pnpm build`\n- `pnpm tsgo:prod`\n- `pnpm test:bundled && pnpm protocol:check`\n- `pnpm ui:i18n:check`\n- `git diff --check origin/main...HEAD`\n- `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode branch --base origin/main --engine codex`\n  - Result: `autoreview clean: no accepted/actionable findings reported`.\n  - Ignored one out-of-scope finding outside the reviewed change.\n\n\n",
